                            </li>
                        </ul>
                        <div class="bottom-line"></div>
                        <h3>Your Dream Home Awaits</h3>
                        <p>
                            Start your journey toward finding a luxury property
                            that truly reflects your lifestyle. Contact us today
                            to explore exclusive properties and let us make your
                            dream a reality.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="padding-top">
                        <a class="btn-primary" href="/us/ga/decatur/luxury-homes"
                        >Luxury Houses Properties</a>
                        <a class="btn-primary" href="/us/ga/decatur/real-estate-agents/contact"
